{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"f9c6551ec5fa5067e89c621655950be92235d8e3a4fb1300e2ded24fe1e0f310","slug":"index-43","location":"/roadmap/qtclass/index.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"量潮课堂工作蓝图","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":2}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/roadmap/qtclass/index.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/roadmap/qtclass/index.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"index.md","url":"/index-def2a771a0ab6463d746654d49355d56.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们的定位","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"uvaXTaidHN"}],"identifier":"id","label":"我们的定位","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"RW3bVTH2FL"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"量潮课堂主要给高校和个人提供教育创新服务和咨询。主要营收来源是技术服务费。","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"i2fsqjSZe7"}],"key":"aZuLIJjkjN"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"由于高校面临教学改革诉求，和市场面临严重的错配和岗位不足，所以有想法的高校纷纷找到我们合作。这是一个市场几乎独一份的服务模式，理论上我们可以为所有需要企业加入教学合作的学校提供类似的服务。","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"YzaMHtAZVm"}],"key":"AMYMzGniFe"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"核心竞争力","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"tTLqfBkbXI"}],"identifier":"id","label":"核心竞争力","html_id":"id-1","implicit":true,"key":"AnOdNmmZfd"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"用四个字概括是\"产教融合\"。具体来说是技术教育能力——能把业界前沿的数据工程和数据挖掘实践转化为可教学可落地的课程体系。","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"PKEQO0vCCO"}],"key":"uu95Jxgusw"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"传统经管和技术教育的思想在急剧过时，而我们刚好卡在了高校急需改革但市场供给稀缺的位置上。","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"OGsUTOv4qQ"}],"key":"JpG5zBUqrB"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们的经营困难","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"ASLZwI4ZN1"}],"identifier":"id","label":"我们的经营困难","html_id":"id-2","implicit":true,"key":"PI85gRbZwh"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在需求侧，高校预算敏感、决策链长，商务谈判和推动落地的成本很高。","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"SaDpEjdNXD"}],"key":"KRBphVerOC"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在供给侧，快速发展的技术和落后保守的高校教育体系之间存在巨大鸿沟。我们需要的人才——既懂技术又懂教学还懂产业的人——几乎从零开始培养。","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"ZFRenjKGqo"}],"key":"S1GKMd0Cx3"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们的应对思路","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"key":"KqMWYpWjIq"}],"identifier":"id","label":"我们的应对思路","html_id":"id-3","implicit":true,"key":"bhqsbwVhgm"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"同样依靠透明、开放、精细的量潮标准化体系，把学校、企业、学生三方的诉求放在同一套工作语言下整合。","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"BMiSIv2oxu"}],"key":"Pbeq29GqXR"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在规模化的关键阶段，核心问题和量潮数据一脉相承：如何确保新人会接受规范而不让规范流失？怎么让老人愿意更新习惯而不守旧？如何平衡各方利益，保持创新能力和教育质量？","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"key":"P8AOmvLOs1"}],"key":"q33zwT2i4C"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这条路应当通向更高的经营效率、更高的杠杆率，而不应该通向虚胖的规模。","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"key":"dLevEMHfwK"}],"key":"CwdEHPX38F"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"平台化是方向","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"CmhZ5TUN4P"}],"identifier":"id","label":"平台化是方向","html_id":"id-4","implicit":true,"key":"cECzTuwFG3"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在 Vibe 工作时代，课程研发和教学执行中的大量细节工作将越来越自动化。课堂团队的主要精力应当放在意义构建——和学校一起设计培养方案、判断什么样的知识结构对学生未来真正有用。","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"key":"zVSMQ49Lcw"}],"key":"XRTA1P46Jm"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"研发系统的目的是解放人力用来创造，而绝非取代人力。课程资料正在和合作学校梳理，未来我们会开源一份量潮版本的课程体系。","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"key":"yCkjHS1VVq"}],"key":"QPtuWy13b0"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"比技术更重要的转型，是使用技术的人转型。整个教学团队需要持续和市场同步，不断把最新的实践经验带入课堂。","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"key":"AM9vk4cSne"}],"key":"Ks7BBhLGj8"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"过往的成功经验","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"key":"bOwATcMPuw"}],"identifier":"id","label":"过往的成功经验","html_id":"id-5","implicit":true,"key":"mDATncU3Vh"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"浙江理工大学计算机系是典型合作案例。他们甚至为了我们打破了企业掏钱给高校合作的传统，第一次主动掏钱给企业做校企合作课程。我们先后负责了生产实习课程、主修的大数据理论课和实践课、大数据微专业整个项目的教学改革工作。","position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"key":"lKU0c1hLwE"}],"key":"qy3KZwpULA"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1},"end":{"line":41,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在我的建议下，数据工程、数据挖掘等工程性和实用性很强的课程得以进入课表，并且大量地引入了我们在业务上的实践，以及最新的使用大模型处理数据的经验。","position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1},"end":{"line":41,"column":1}},"key":"AJfuvDoAsY"}],"key":"jdihuyFBtU"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":1},"end":{"line":43,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最重要的改变是创始人从\"专制君主\"向\"立宪君主\"、公司从\"人治\"向\"法治\"转变带来的杠杆效应。放弃中心化的决策习惯，建立去中心化的、分布式的决策新习惯，是规模化的必经之路。","position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":1},"end":{"line":43,"column":1}},"key":"BXr3N0cESM"}],"key":"AVTgpBMzmo"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":45,"column":1},"end":{"line":45,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们过往的成功经验，是在一次一次地技术浪潮中抓住空隙钻过去，从而一轮又一轮地苟住没倒闭。保持这样的思考是最根源的动力。","position":{"start":{"line":45,"column":1},"end":{"line":45,"column":1}},"key":"eLjyDXncaP"}],"key":"N9BPzgtskL"}],"key":"N2c7d9HBP5"}],"key":"LQcY9SMlD0"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}